rows.label: qst202104_0010
rows.name: This is momentous!

rows.label: qst202104_0020
rows.name:
*Gasp*
But what is this?

rows.label: qst202104_0030
rows.name: She's in her own little world.

rows.label: qst202104_0040
rows.name: Classic Shiki.

rows.label: qst202104_0050
rows.name:
Geez...
Shiki, stop running off by yourself...

rows.label: qst202104_0060
rows.name: Hold up, Nia.

rows.label: qst202104_0070
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: qst202104_0080
rows.name: There's something inside the room...

rows.label: qst202104_0090
rows.name: An enemy?!

rows.label: qst202104_0100
rows.name: It would appear to be the room's guardian...

rows.label: qst202104_0110
rows.name: Shiki! It's not safe in there!

rows.label: qst202104_0120
rows.name: Save your breath, she's not listening.

rows.label: qst202104_0130
rows.name:
Bad news!
Going for Shiki!

rows.label: qst202104_0140
rows.name: Shiki! Run!

rows.label: qst202104_0150
rows.name:
Stop the shouting...
Can't you see you're breaking my concentration?

rows.label: qst202104_0160
rows.name: Whah-!

rows.label: qst202104_0170
rows.name:
How dare you come in here and interfere with my research?!
I was just getting to the good bits, too...

rows.label: qst202104_0180
rows.name:
You're not gonna put a damper on my
curiosity and studiousness! That's a promise!

rows.label: qst202104_0190
rows.name:
Understood? Get the picture?
Shut up and let me work!

rows.label: qst202104_0200
rows.name:
We probably shouldn't let Shiki
have all the fun.

rows.label: qst202104_0210
rows.name: Let's get in there and help, Rex!
